<text top="104" left="108" width="4" height="14" font="6"> </text>
<text top="125" left="72" width="19" height="14" font="4">17.</text>
<text top="125" left="91" width="4" height="14" font="5"> </text>
<text top="125" left="108" width="436" height="14" font="6">As  this  matter  must  be  disposed  of  urgently,  I  now  invite  the </text>
