<text top="494" left="90" width="19" height="14" font="6">(2)</text>
<text top="494" left="109" width="4" height="15" font="9"> </text>
<text top="494" left="126" width="418" height="14" font="6">The  petitioner  shall  be  at  liberty  to  file  and  serve  the </text>
